          "description": "Really excellent dental experience.  I had an emergency with an implant that I had done at a different office. The dentist and dental assistant were excellent, connected to my records at the other office and very quickly fixed the issue without any pain and double checked everything related to fit, bite, comfort, etc. Everything was very smooth from numbing to tools/devices, filling. Seems like at the dentist there is always something that requires a second or third attempt but this time everything was done right the first time quickly and efficiently. I recommend both the dentist and dental assistant that helped me today.",
